gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 119, 76ers 107
gameRecap.excerpt: Stephen Curry leads the way with 37 points, eight rebounds, seven assists and eight 3PM as the Warriors defeat the 76ers, 119-107.  Jonathan Kuminga (26 points, seven rebounds, three steals) and Andrew Wiggins (23 points, five rebounds, four assists) added a combined 49 points in the victory.  Tobias Harris tallied 26 points and 10 rebounds for the 76ers, while Joel Embiid added 14 points and seven rebounds.
